.TH "new_rtas_args" 9 "new_rtas_args" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
new_rtas_args \- Allocates rtas args
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct rtas_args *" new_rtas_args
.BI "(int cpu "  ","
.BI "unsigned long limit "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cpu" 12
CPU number
.IP "limit" 12
Memory limit for this allocation
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Allocates a struct rtas_args and return it's pointer,
if not in Hypervisor mode
.SH "RETURN"
Pointer to allocated rtas_args
NULL if CPU in Hypervisor Mode
